{% else -%}
[§ 33b Abs. 3 EStG](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/estg/__33b.html)
grants a flat allowance for disability, scaled by the Grad der
Behinderung (GdB); § 33b Abs. 3 Satz 3 EStG carries a special amount of
EUR 7,400 for hilflose / blinde Menschen. The 2025 schedule values come
from the Behinderten-Pauschbetragsgesetz [(BGBl. I 2020 S. 2770)](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/bgbl_i_2020/2770.html),
which doubled the rates effective 2021 and carries unchanged into 2025.

[§ 33b Abs. 5 EStG](https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/estg/__33b.html)
permits **transferring** a qualifying child's Pauschbetrag to the
parents when the child does not claim it on their own assessment
(§ 33b Abs. 5 Satz 1 EStG). The transferred allowance attaches to the
parents' assessment under the § 2 Abs. 5 EStG ordering (§ 33b Abs. 5
Satz 2 EStG).

